### distrXXX family version 2.2

+ ladealles.R now loads both .r and .R files
+ new util in compare.R: compare() to compare two objects slot-wise, recursively... 
+ new util in showAllFiles.R:  
  showAllFiles() concatenates all files of same kind in one output (like NEWS, TOBEDONE)
+ new util in showsvnlog.R:  
  using bash-script readsvnlog.sh , showsvnlog() reads out svn log information 
  / works with bash shell (@Matthias: pls check Linux!) 
+ modified DESCRIPTIONutils.R  --- now uses gsub()
+ updated README-R-utils





